>>>At some point, if you're lucky (?), they are so proud of it, they tell
>>>you
allllll about it. If you're lucky, they DON'T show you. This just happened
yesterday.Tuck<<<

OH NOOOO! Oh, this has me in stitches! My cheeks are burning now from
laughing so hard! This will be my Ethan. He's still young, three next
month, but he is in LOVE with his 'dinky'. Calls it a teepee though, which
I find so amusingly cute! He's also my streaker, so I imagine he will be
proud to show it off for quite some time to come. Grosses his big sister
out beyond belief! HAHAHAHA! OUCH, this hurts!

Jennifer, thanking Tuck for the great laugh...I needed it!
